{"tid":1672500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"GPHONE快D殺去油尖民政署啦","createTime":"2019-10-24T06:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T08:34:31.000Z","uid":6497,"like":119,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"73e09af832f87de78a68a27cb34f4c2b8707829e","tid":1672500,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/24/P2019102400434.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F24%2FP2019102400434.htm&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=15972bd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/24/P2019102400434.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n選舉管理委員會公告<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代選舉管理委員會發出：<br />\n<br />\n  選舉管理委員會（選管會）今日（十月二十四日）獲悉南區民政事務專員因病休假，油尖旺民政事務專員蔡亮由今日起兼任該職位，直至另行通知為止。根據今年九月六日的憲報公告，出任南區民政事務專員的人員被委任為有關選區的選舉主任，故此由今日起，署理南區民政事務專員會成為有關選區的選舉主任。<br />\n<br />\n  另外，選管會將於今晚為二○一九年區議會一般選舉的候選人及其代理人舉辦簡介會，簡介會前會為候選人進行抽籤程序，以決定候選人在選票上的排列次序。由於南區海怡西選區尚有一份提名表格在處理中，當區的選舉主任會於稍後另行安排為該選區進行抽籤。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年10月24日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間14時44分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉左油尖旺蔡亮<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201408/24/P201408210459_photo_1073250.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201408%2F24%2FP201408210459_photo_1073250.JPG&h=ce8cfe9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e71671541925379878c7814986db83840b83b24a","tid":1672500,"uid":19552,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 射波避制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67e402757a498303a5294d49882f495bf990afe","tid":1672500,"uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"跟住到呢個臨時SL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71c82e56f6a4cdc1