sg":"痴撚線 射波避制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"射波英文點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffa126d295aa65f76507ad00a7d5c337b6ce22d","tid":1672500,"uid":140949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬周佩芬扮sick leave，由一個大陸人頂上DQ go home, 咁馬周佩芬有無責任呢？算唔算協助極權政府剝奪香港市民參選權？</span></span>"},{"pid":"76730c495dad998ef4a1d07cd4b3089c51417941","tid":1672500,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdf69bf903efb71b2bbf90bebeb4d628692622c","tid":1672500,"uid":11008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:36:06.000Z","msg":"咁撚驚比人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩事咪上大灣區囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ba8e74bd0f2f04e6a4fd1ccf7b8843d14efec3","tid":1672500,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:36:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"313f2c42252599659f34e158731d926061a18311","tid":1672500,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ffa126d295aa65f76507ad00a7d5c337b6ce22d","tid":1672500,"uid":140949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬周佩芬扮sick leave，由一個大陸人頂上DQ go home, 咁馬周佩芬有無責任呢？算唔算協助極權政府剝奪香港市民參選權？</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Gphone</span></span>"},{"pid":"66cd77e91205ea1a47ef429c05bedbe9d63b492f","tid":1672500,"uid":10008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ffa126d295aa65f76507ad00a7d5c337b6ce22d","tid":1672500,"uid":140949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬周佩芬扮sick leave，由一個大陸人頂上DQ go home, 咁馬周佩芬有無責任呢？算唔算協助極權政府剝奪香港市民參選權？</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:36:32.000Z","msg":"所以最終DQ佢都需要制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7e43f20b82ae06f751fd808424f41d12db1f58","tid":1672500,"uid":13690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯練膽大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fef5fe8875950a28d9276c2b6867ac4814b8e6c","tid":1672500,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"[控場師] 為左更有組織，我地整左幾支新旗，求百屌成材<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672240</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家入黎俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家對旗手小隊已經唔陌生<br />\n鑑於近日戰術更改，我哋收到意見，稱旗手缺乏進攻旗以迎合近日抗爭路向。有見及此，我哋推出咗三枝進攻用新旗等大家俾啲意見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oeDL6K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oeDL6K.jpg&h=acd10ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橙旗 - 進攻 Attack<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">當狗後退時或前線有共識可進攻時使用</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFrUZ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFrUZ9.jpg&h=b56326b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃旗 - 列陣 Embattle<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">狗上gear，我地需要上gear時用</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8DpGFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8DpGFe.jpg&h=9db4f232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啡旗 - 堅守陣地 Stand Your Ground<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">堅守地點，以防敵方從中段空位突擊</span><br />\n<br />\n以下係溫故知新 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofd5q60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fofd5q60.jpg&h=92e53e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綠旗 - 可前進 Go Forward<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">前線安全準備推進亦需要中後排各位，大家判斷後請準備gear up與前線一起</span>前進<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFsmJTZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFsmJTZ.jpg&h=14c19d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅旗 - 停 STOP<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後退或前進到一定時候需要暫停一下，請提高警覺隨時準備對應任何突發狀況</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7vb57q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7vb57q.jpg&h=6f00eab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃旗 - 企鬆啲 Keep Distance<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">咪手講「左右留中」時，配合預留中間位置俾前線手足，中後排要企鬆啲，最少要預留1-1.5個手位，為前線預留充足空間。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gO2NEsv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgO2NEsv.jpg&h=81fde43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍旗 - 慢慢後退Back Away Slowly<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">當狗隻施行密集式催淚攻擊時，請保持隊形冷靜數住一二一二後退<br />\n亦要睇情況加快腳步</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yL1iL7z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyL1iL7z.jpg&h=61e3c536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑旗 - 急撤 Danger Back Off<br />\n黑旗由「急退前線危險」改成「急撤」。過去黑旗喺前線真係頂唔撚緊最壞情況之下先會舉起，但實測後發現，現場往往舉旗時間不足，舉起時容易錯失最佳急撤時機（原諒旗手都係要跑嘅普通人）。所以，<span style=\"color: red;\">新黑旗將用於旗手範圍內，在出現重大危險</span>（例如係裝甲車或水炮車已就位），<span style=\"color: red;\">前線需要大量空間方便走避時用</span>。<br />\n我地亦收到前線意見，急撤時，後排走太快、中排走太慢，令前中後線經常出現斷層，狗隻便會從中突擊/包抄，望各位進退有度，齊上齊落，留意旗手指示。<br />\n另外，前線亦希望中排急撤時勿再用「一二一二」拖慢節奏，望各位留意🙏🏼<br />\n<br />\n最後，好重點好重點同大家講，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地旗手隊同前線係有共識嘅</span></span></ins>，同埋我地會<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">有咪手嘅配合去補充旗唔夠嘅資訊</span></ins>，所以大家到時要多多留意咪手指引。<br />\n<br />\n各位前線同後排嘅手足<br />\n希望大家不分勇和<br />\n不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"52873499fe7b9666848513c05786528d925bf81c","tid":1672500,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"辭職啦，咁樣射波仲有面繼續做"},{"pid":"c118a53297c093ecd7beb1568873e8cab1c5c9d6","tid":1672500,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:49:52.000Z","msg":"仲有，你估唔係你宣布DQ就無事咩，成個確認過程成兩個禮拜都唔確認就一樣係幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ca12e6e691e6a7bbac6d13cf54759c1df2ca0a","tid":1672500,"uid":46447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"dq gphone既話全部都要制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2710432bfae1606c14c6178b081baaaa73f98b53","tid":1672500,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:54:12.000Z","msg":"根本唔洗急<br />\nGPHONE咁出名邊個DQ佢死邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01bd20b4f01e3586cf079579f4d1716d50ea519","tid":1672500,"uid":164511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ca12e6e691e6a7bbac6d13cf54759c1df2ca0a","tid":1672500,"uid":46447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"dq gphone既話全部都要制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"有份PRINT 張表既都應該要制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf29e50d6c5053e07abacc35640b374f09b9ec2","tid":1672500,"uid":276393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"最早報名<br />\n最遲都未通知<br />\nDllm"},{"pid":"cc27e25a3fb6d53a10a3eae003cee99d4adddb68","tid":1672500,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8a9e7ee4b6437ca288436f552fa0e7aa2f56cc","tid":1672500,"uid":33028,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0515c4fa31609d448ef349bc11311ec0a982f223","tid":1672500,"uid":277912,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"73e09af832f87de78a68a27cb34f4c2b8707829e","tid":1672500,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/24/P2019102400434.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F24%2FP2019102400434.htm&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=15972bd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/24/P2019102400434.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n選舉管理委員會公告<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代選舉管理委員會發出：<br />\n<br />\n  選舉管理委員會（選管會）今日（十月二十四日）獲悉南區民政事務專員因病休假，油尖旺民政事務專員蔡亮由今日起兼任該職位，直至另行通知為止。根據今年九月六日的憲報公告，出任南區民政事務專員的人員被委任為有關選區的選舉主任，故此由今日起，署理南區民政事務專員會成為有關選區的選舉主任。<br />\n<br />\n  另外，選管會將於今晚為二○一九年區議會一般選舉的候選人及其代理人舉辦簡介會，簡介會前會為候選人進行抽籤程序，以決定候選人在選票上的排列次序。由於南區海怡西選區尚有一份提名表格在處理中，當區的選舉主任會於稍後另行安排為該選區進行抽籤。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年10月24日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間14時44分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉左油尖旺蔡亮<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201408/24/P201408210459_photo_1073250.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201408%2F24%2FP201408210459_photo_1073250.JPG&h=ce8cfe9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"聴個名都估到佢係G那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"英文名Laura Liang Aron"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"Aron係佢老公姓<br />\n可能美國人黎<br />\n所以唔撚驚制裁"}]}